      "role": "user",
      "content": "That looks pretty good, thanks. Could you actually make it sound a little bit more personal though? Maybe add a sentence or two acknowledging that even though he wasn't the right fit for the cloud architecture stuff, he's definitely someone we might want to keep in mind for the future if our needs change? I don't want him to feel like he's just a number.",
